name: CLOAK
description: CLOAK start with a collection of 1111 avatar will include 54 1/1 NFT’s. Each CLOAK is unique and each will carry desirable traits that can be used throughout our ecosystem. Holding CLOAK will give you exclusive access in MILO’s World and a membership card with full access to the community and exclusive rights. Also holding our first generation of CLOAK will get you all future generations NFTs for free by airdrop. (Always, subject to the last holder of CLOAK)
